# Files NOT uploaded to Cloud Build by `gcloud builds submit`.
#
# WHY THIS EXISTS: without it, `gcloud builds submit` uploads the whole source
# tree, which includes iac/.terraform/ — the OpenTofu provider plugin cache,
# ~119M after `tofu init`. That bloats every build upload (full or targeted)
# and is never needed in any image (the Dockerfiles bake in only what they
# COPY). `#!include:.gitignore` pulls in the .gitignore patterns; the explicit
# entries below are belt-and-suspenders so the exclusion does not depend on
# .gitignore include semantics.
.git
iac/.terraform/
#!include:.gitignore
